something she'll later regret

952
01:11:13,132 --> 01:11:16,092
with the fiancé's
better-looking chum. Let's go.

953
01:11:21,598 --> 01:11:24,684
Half a crown says
Alan bollockses this up entirely.

954
01:11:24,768 --> 01:11:26,227
No bet.

955
01:11:26,311 --> 01:11:28,479
- Alan Turing has a theory.
- He has many.

956
01:11:29,273 --> 01:11:31,482
He believes that the regulations
against men and women

957
01:11:31,608 --> 01:11:34,027
working side by side are sound

958
01:11:34,111 --> 01:11:36,571
because such proximity
will necessarily lead to romance.

959
01:11:36,655 --> 01:11:39,991
- Er, what? No, I don't. I...
- However, I disagree.

960
01:11:40,117 --> 01:11:41,617
- You do?
