- A.
- A.

1062
01:16:44,046 --> 01:16:45,087
- I.
- I.

1063
01:16:45,213 --> 01:16:46,339
- C.
- C.

1064
01:16:46,423 --> 01:16:47,423
- T.
- T.

1065
01:16:47,507 --> 01:16:48,507
- R.
- R.

1066
01:16:48,592 --> 01:16:49,592
- I.
- I.

1067
01:16:49,676 --> 01:16:50,676
- S.
- S.

1068
01:16:50,761 --> 01:16:51,761
- O.
- O.

1069
01:16:51,845 --> 01:16:52,845
- A.
- A.

1070
01:16:52,929 --> 01:16:53,929
- Y.
- Y.

1071
01:16:54,014 --> 01:16:55,097
- R.
- R.

1072
01:16:55,182 --> 01:16:56,599
- I.
- I.

1073
01:17:02,397 --> 01:17:06,525
"KMS Jaguar ist aufpunkt... is directed
to 53 degrees 24 minutes north

1074
01:17:06,610 --> 01:17:10,196
"and aufpunkt one degree west."

1075
01:17:11,698 --> 01:17:13,115
Heil Hitler.

1076
01:17:18,288 --> 01:17:21,874
Turns out that's the only German
you need to know to break Enigma.

1077
01:17:29,883 --> 01:17:31,300
Yes!

1078
01:17:49,986 --> 01:17:51,487
Come here.

1079
01:18:24,688 --> 01:18:26,188
M.

1080
01:18:26,273 --> 01:18:27,690
A.

1081
01:18:27,774 --> 01:18:29,191
Y.

1082
01:18:29,276 --> 01:18:30,693
- I.
- I.

1083
01:18:30,777 --> 01:18:33,279
- T. R.
- R.

1084
01:18:33,363 --> 01:18:34,864
- O.
- T.

1085
01:18:34,948 --> 01:18:36,365
T.

1086
01:18:36,533 --> 01:18:37,616
- A.
- A.

1087
01:18:37,701 --> 01:18:38,826
- H.
- H.

1088
